High volume, low intensity, aerobic foundation. Easy running dominant; the quality run is a fartlek (no structured tempo in Base). Strength base in lifting; minimal hybrid.
Hybrid station library for this mesocycle: ski erg, row erg, assault bike, wall balls, farmers carry.

