Body weight: 80 kg
Experience — running: intermediate, hybrid: intermediate, lifting: intermediate
Training classification: non_highly_trained
Training days: mon, tue, wed, thu, fri
Benchmarks: 5K 22:00, 10K 46:00, 5RM squat 140, 5RM bench 100, 5RM deadlift 180, 2k ski 7:30, 2k row 7:20

MESOCYCLE: PEAK
High intensity, HYROX-specific simulation, volume drops. Threshold and interval runs plus a weekly progression run at true race-effort finishes; maximum hybrid specificity.
